{"tid":1617804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成功令全office人都戴口罩！！！","createTime":"2019-10-04T01:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T04:07:10.000Z","uid":154039,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3af125675f53a08a0269fa5ecc552e761dadedc6","tid":1617804,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"（我係標題黨）<br />\n<br />\n屌你<br />\n今朝搭巴士得三個人戴。<br />\n<br />\n我嚴重警告世人，同我做以下工作：<br />\n<br />\n1. 出文宣，貼連儂，周街貼<br />\n講既唔單止係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蒙面法</span></span>，仲帶有係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急法</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n蒙面唔會影響民生，但政府開先例用緊急法，佢以後都可以無啦啦唔緊法律程序郁個社會，甚麼外匯管制，到時人地外資走曬就真冚家產。咁先逼到世人戴口罩反蒙面法，反緊急法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. Lunch time同我係街到派口罩<br />\n每間office，每間鋪頭都要放盒口罩，方便大家戴！！！係街到學隔離post巴打拎大聲公派口罩，得左！！！各位黃店店主係盒口罩隔離仲可以解釋下蒙面法緊急法既影響，警世班港豬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做野啊！我要番去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民口罩</span></span>既時期！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民口罩唔係得10月4，係以後。 日撚日都要戴啊屌你！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n辛苦各位手足，一齊努力。"},{"pid":"b739d2aee5156fba29f91425b926753700ce51ce","tid":1617804,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:00:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dfa67e26fa87c42fc81bcef3720918fbe6bb786","tid":1617804,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"210bb27e5aa1a784c6436f1555800adb299700dc","tid":1617804,"uid":202904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c2d6bb12747dae74b2414a570b40b8f7bc5c601","tid":1617804,"uid":198783,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T02:02:56.000Z","msg":"標題黨死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},